%3Cimg%20align%3D%22LEFT%22%20hspace%3D%2210%22%3E%0AIt%20is%20hard%20experience%20to%20taking%20picture%20of%20this%20toilet.%3Cbr%3E%0AThere%20are%20many%20vomit%20and%20excreta%20by%20drunks%20at%20Saturday%20night%20of%20December.%3Cbr%3E%0AI%20stopped%20breathing%20when%20I%20take%20pictures.%3Cbr%3E%0A%3Cbr%20clear%3D%22all%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%0A%0A%3Chr%20noshade%3D%22%22%3E%0A%0A%3Ca%20href%3D%22index_e.htm%22%3EBack%20to%20homepage%3C%2Fa%3E%0A%0A%0A%3C%2Fbody%3E%0A%3C%2Fbody%3E%0A%3C%2Fhtml%3E"
